        Up Items.

        Picked Up Items Are Displayed At The Top Of The Screen,

        You
        Can Select By Tapping.


        - Item Use

        If You Tap A Suspicious
        Place With An Item Selected,

        May Be Used.


        - Show Items
        Larger

